 a lean way to develop an alternative-energy car. It was fun to toy\naround with that idea and imagine ways to enable this. Given the knowledge I\nhave collected working at Nordic and as the son of an automobile industry\nveteran I could add some insights."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"https://twitter.com/coderbyheart/status/965954967256358914?embed&conversation=none"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/coderbyheart/status/965954967256358914?embed&conversation=none","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"https://twitter.com/RidingWolf/status/965954663924322304?embed"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/RidingWolf/status/965954663924322304?embed","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"In the session on Continuous Deployment we talked about the do's and don'ts.\nBasically: you want your CI runners to be\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Phoenix Servers"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://martinfowler.com/bliki/PhoenixServer.html","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":".\n"},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Chris Dr√§ger"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/_chris_draeger_","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" who hosted this session\nfound "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"LambdaCD"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"http://www.lambda.cd/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" to be his tool of choice. I would\nrecommend "},{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"Travis"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://travis-ci.org/","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" + Makefiles to solve this."}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"https://twitter.com/coderbyheart/status/965962746415206401?embed&conversation=none"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/coderbyheart/status/965962746415206401?embed&conversation=none","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"How to Kanban better"}],"tagName":"em","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":" started as a question on how to improve Kanban but this\nsession quickly turned into a team clinic, where we tried to find ways for a\nteam to improve their internal shortcomings, which were just being revealed by\nusing Kanban:"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"https://twitter.com/coderbyheart/status/965964932960354305?embed&conversation=none"}],"tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://twitter.com/coderbyheart/status/965964932960354305?embed&conversation=none","target":"_blank","rel":["nofollow","noreferrer"]},"type":"element"}],"tagName":"p","properties":{},"type":"element"},{"children":[],"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[{"children":[],"tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":